        "slide_deck_sidecar": "## Slide Deck Sidecar\n```markdown\n---\nbook: \"Acts\"\nchapter: \"14\"\nsection: \"2\"\nvisual_palette: sepia parchment, dust-light, ochre\n---\n\n# Acts 14:2 — The Anatomy of Gospel Opposition\nThis single verse provides a crucial, repeatable template for understanding the nature of spiritual opposition to the church's mission: it is active, intentional, and targets the soul.\n\n*Slide deck: 5 sections, 5 total sub-slides, ≤5 bullets per slide.*\n",
